@{
    ViewBag.Title = "About Arafat Paints & Varnish Ltd";
    ViewBag.Message = "Welcome to the world of premium paints and coatings!";
}

<main aria-labelledby="title" class="container">
    <h2 id="title" class="text-center my-4">@ViewBag.Title</h2>
    <h3 class="text-center mb-4">@ViewBag.Message</h3>

    <div class="jumbotron bg-primary text-white text-center">
        <h4>Welcome to Arafat Paints & Varnish Ltd</h4>
        <p>Your trusted partner in providing top-quality paints and coatings for homes, businesses, and industrial applications.</p>
    </div>

    <p>Welcome to <strong>Arafat Paints & Varnish Ltd</strong>, your trusted partner in providing top-quality paints and coatings for homes, businesses, and industrial applications. With over a decade of experience, we pride ourselves on delivering durable, vibrant, and eco-friendly paint solutions to meet all of your decorative and functional needs.</p>

    <p>We are committed to helping you enhance the beauty and longevity of your spaces with our wide range of innovative products. Whether you're looking for exterior or interior paints, coatings, or specialized finishes, we have something to suit every project.</p>

    <h4 class="mt-5">Our Mission</h4>
    <p>Our mission is to provide customers with the best paints and coatings, backed by superior customer service, sustainability, and technical expertise. We strive to contribute to a greener world by using eco-friendly ingredients and reducing our environmental footprint through responsible practices.</p>

    <h4 class="mt-5">Our Values</h4>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Quality:</strong> We believe in offering only the highest quality products for your projects.</li>
        <li><strong>Innovation:</strong> We continuously evolve our product offerings, incorporating the latest trends and technologies.</li>
        <li><strong>Customer Commitment:</strong> Our customers’ satisfaction is our top priority. We listen to your needs and deliver on promises.</li>
        <li><strong>Environmental Responsibility:</strong> We are dedicated to preserving the environment and creating products that are safe for people and nature.</li>
    </ul>

    <h4 class="mt-5">Why Choose Arafat Paints?</h4>
    <p>When you choose Arafat Paints, you’re choosing a brand you can trust for quality, reliability, and expertise. Here’s why:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>High-performance products for both residential and commercial applications.</li>
        <li>A wide range of color options and finishes to suit every style.</li>
        <li>Eco-friendly and non-toxic paint solutions for a healthier environment.</li>
        <li>Personalized service with a focus on meeting the specific needs of each client.</li>
        <li>Expert technical support to guide you through your painting projects.</li>
    </ul>

    <p>We are proud to be a part of many successful projects over the years and look forward to continuing our tradition of excellence. Thank you for choosing Arafat Paints & Varnish Ltd – where quality meets color!</p>
</main>

@section Styles {
    <style>
        .jumbotron {
            background-color: #007bff;
            border-radius: 0;
        }

        h2 {
            color: #007bff;
        }

        ul {
            list-style-type: none;
            padding-left: 0;
        }

            ul li {
                padding: 5px 0;
            }
    </style>
}
